    <RootNamespace>Rdn</RootNamespace>
    <NoWarn>$(NoWarn);CS8969</NoWarn>
    <PackageId>Rdn</PackageId>
    <Description>A .NET implementation of RDN (Rich Data Notation) â€” a JSON superset with native dates, durations, regex, binary, Maps, Sets, and special numerics. Fork of System.Text.Json with familiar API.</Description>
